article.description: Long Beach St. 76, E. New Mexico 54
article.headline: Long Beach St. 76, E. New Mexico 54
article.linkText: Long Beach St. 76, E. New Mexico 54
article.story: LONG BEACH, Calif. -- James Ennis scored 15 points and Larry Anderson added 14 points and seven rebounds as Long Beach State defeated Eastern New Mexico 76-54 on Monday night. Eugene Phelps had 11 points and Casper Ware 10 for the 49ers (6-6). Stefan Miribal had 19 points and Aaron Edwards 14 points and seven rebounds for the Division II Greyhounds (9-4). Eastern New Mexico had first-half scoreless stretches of 4:58, 3:18 and 2:52 as Long Beach State built a 40-36 halftime lead. The Greyhounds got no closer than seven points in the second half. Long Beach State enjoyed a 36-28 rebounding edge and outscored Eastern New Mexico 48-28 in the paint.
